Field descriptions:
- mythic_items: Mythic tier items (legendary grade, one per build)
- strong_counters: Champions that counter me (my win rate < 50% against them)
- weak_counters: Champions I counter (my win rate > 50% against them)
- counters_meta: Optional metadata about counter sample sufficiency. Present only when strong_counters or weak_counters are empty due to insufficient matchup sample; include this field when querying counters so empty-result cases are explained instead of silent.
- damage_type: Champion damage type (AD=Attack Damage, AP=Ability Power, BOTH=Hybrid)
- skill_combos: Recommended champion skill combos with demo video links
- skill_masteries: Priority order for maxing abilities (Q/W/E)

