Field descriptions:
- position.*.is_rip: Whether champion is considered RIP (weak/unplayable) in this position
- position.*.role_rate: Percentage of games this champion plays in this role vs other roles
- position.*.kda: KDA ratio (Kills + Assists / Deaths)
- position.*.tier: Tier ranking (1=OP, 2=Strong, 3=Good, 4=Average, 5=Weak)
